{"tid":1540012,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"成班都on99，人地都動議撤回啦","createTime":"2019-09-04T10:41:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T11:15:54.000Z","uid":230681,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"bb800a73a49e3def5c23e483984ef50d5b5c841f","tid":1540012,"uid":230681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:41:55.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母呀！咩叫<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求，缺一不可呀！</span></span><br />\n 佢動議咋 未撚係撤回呀<br />\n就算撤回咗又點撚樣呀？<br />\n唔撚記得d狗打人打到傻撚咗？<br />\n<br />\n咪撚再問袋唔袋呀<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔撚袋！唔撚割！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一日唔為死士同義士取回公道<br />\n場運動都唔會有完既一日<br />\n各位手足 我地今日行到嚟呢一步唔簡單<br />\n係犧牲咗好多人既前途、時間、心力、金錢<br />\n先至嚇撚到個正苦有今日既決定<br />\n<br />\n咁即係代表咩呀？<br />\n即係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">代表我地做緊野無白費！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嚟緊要做既 <br />\n係更加<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大力宣傳黑驚既濫捕濫權暴力<br />\n鄉黑同黑驚點樣無差別打9市民</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港！時代革命！<br />\n五大訴求！缺一不可！<br />\n香港警察！知法犯法！<br />\n香港人！加油！</span></span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QDmWyQc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQDmWyQc.png&h=397a946e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LA9dA3y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLA9dA3y.png&h=9f226129&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nOKtpWU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnOKtpWU.png&h=072e44fb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9oK5saf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9oK5saf.png&h=5c0efeb9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/npaHuoB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnpaHuoB.png&h=f2ef071f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"15f53710236159071e7d298b7e7a2fe14eb07003","tid":1540012,"uid":38165,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:42:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"14463326aa5feb10b1e03991d79c8cf6e6dd4064","tid":1540012,"uid":289649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:42:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">林鄭宣布撤回送中條例的六大陰謀</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1539227\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1539227</a><br />\n快啲同我入黎睇曬佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f7129a8e909457be508c37f26a9d32f447bc5ca","tid":1540012,"uid":161457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:42:16.000Z","msg":"建議死線攻擊中資企業 增加籌碼 如果仲係會回應 增加破壞程度 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p5zk0uW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp5zk0uW.jpg&h=952bdf35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5vY2uoj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5vY2uoj.jpg&h=639f13c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/waNVPoB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwaNVPoB.jpg&h=1156d0a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6a2bfb723eef718705d4903d6409efabc6e14522","tid":1540012,"uid":24443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:42:25.000Z","msg":"唔撚囉返幾件警畜祭旗 點消心頭之恨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><